headline: Keysight’s SOS Enterprise Targets AI Data Governance And Investor Stickiness
summary: Keysight Technologies (NYSE:KEYS) has introduced SOS Enterprise, an engineering data management platform focused on automated data governance and traceability. The platform is designed to help engineering teams prepare for large scale AI adoption and meet growing regulatory compliance needs across complex, multi site operations. SOS Enterprise centers on data lineage, compliance support, and secure collaboration to streamline engineering workflows. For investors watching Keysight...
